Privacy Policy for Certy Testing

Effective Date: 12 March 2025

Introduction
We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our application.

Information We Collect
When you connect your Instagram account to our application, we may collect the following information:

Your Instagram user ID

Access token for your Instagram account

Public profile information and media (if permission is granted)

How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information solely to enable the features of our application, such as:

Allowing you to post photos to your Instagram account

Accessing and displaying your Instagram media

Data Security
We take appropriate technical and organizational measures to secure your data and protect it from unauthorized access, loss, misuse, or alteration.

Sharing of Information
We do not share, sell, or distribute your information to third parties unless required by law.

Your Rights
You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information at any time. If you wish to exercise these rights, please contact us at [Your Contact Email].

Changes to This Policy
We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.

Contact Information
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at kowe06@gmail.com.

By using our application, you agree to the collection and use of your information as described in this policy.

